ok reader supports a wide range of reading material. Aside from eBooks, you can access your favorite newspapers and magazines and borrow digital books from your local library. For international and multi-lingual readers, the Nook Simple Touch GlowLight also offers multi-language support."]},"id":"d1a5c1ce-3f64-4690-b27a-41595ae8b955","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"3a0c5176-bb4c-4694-ad37-ff01d6bd3332","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/kVjkYs5xjHBFGkK4heDFyM.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"e NOOK Simple Touch GlowLight offers handy features that allow you to personalize your reading experience for maximum comfort and enjoyment. To begin with, the device comes with the two features we deem most important in electronic readers: automatic sync and adjustable fonts. When you download a new book on your digital reader, it automatically syncs to all your devices that have the NOOK app installed. This way you can access your entire library even when you don’t have the eReader with you. Seven text sizes and six font styles allow you to choose the exact font style you like.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/53374-nook-simple-touch4.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kVjkYs5xjHBFGkK4heDFyM.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"kVjkYs5xjHBFGkK4heDFyM","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kVjkYs5xjHBFGkK4heDFyM.jpg","alt":""},"id":"22a2b1d0-129f-4c35-ab9a-aab4f1d5a67e","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["We also like the intuitive bookmarking function and the integrated dictionary included on the GlowLight Nook. Using it is simply a matter of pressing Look Up Word on the touchscreen then using the up, down, right and left arrows to navigate to the word in question. Tap Look Up and the definition appears superimposed on the reading screen."]},"id":"780a1d1a-6fec-4fc8-87c5-5d97e0b898c7","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"c8572710-27f0-4642-9741-6020a2613f